nodes.text: Stren Colo was a Human male that lived during the Galactic Civil War. He was an Imperial officer stationed in Kachirho on the forest planet of Kashyyyk. When not doing direct service for the Empire, Colo worked as a bounty hunter, helping to track down two wanted criminals, Jessk and a Human named Dorn. Tien Wallub and Belga Daeri were his most trusted contacts.
